  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/misc-gadgets/\" rel=\"tag\">精彩杂录</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/02/apple-acquires-passif-semiconductor/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/08/iphone-5-2012-09-14-600-21.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n继 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/20/apple-hopstop/\">HopStop</a> 和 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/20/apple-acquires-location-based-data-startup-locationary/\">Locationary</a> 之后，苹果的血拼之旅仍在继续，而这一次他们收购的是硅谷无线芯片制造商 Passif Semiconductor。<a href=\"http://jessicalessin.com/2013/08/01/exclusive-apple-recently-acquired-low-energy-chipmaker-passif/\">Jessica Lessin</a> 最早报道了这个消息，之后 <a href=\"http://allthingsd.com/20130801/apple-confirms-acquisition-of-passif-semiconductor/?mod=atdtweet\">AllThingsD</a> 也从 Apple 那里得到了确认。据悉 Passif Semiconductor 目前正在开发低功耗通讯芯片，其中包括有与低功耗<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/bluetooth4.0\">蓝牙 4.0</a> 相关的技术。这样一来便不免会让人联想到传说中的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/02/13/bloomberg-apple-watch-rumor/\">iWatch</a>，苹果在做的会不会是这个打算呢？当然，按照他们的说法「购买小科技公司是常有的事」，至于背后的目的嘛，以后你就会知道啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/08/01/apple-acquires-passif-semiconductor/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://jessicalessin.com/2013/08/01/exclusive-apple-recently-acquired-low-energy-chipmaker-passif/\" target=\"_blank\">Jessica Lessin</a>、<a href=\"http://allthingsd.com/20130801/apple-confirms-acquisition-of-passif-semiconductor/?mod=atdtweet\" target=\"_blank\">AllThingsD</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/02/apple-acquires-passif-semiconductor/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20684496/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文